items.title: Awesome Ciandcd
items.content_text:
### Dev env

*   [T.A.D.S. boilerplate (‚≠ê779)](https://github.com/Thomvaill/tads-boilerplate) A boilerplate to setup a Docker Swarm environment with Ansible

### Build And Release System

*   [Drone CI](https://drone.io/) Drone is a Continuous Delivery system built on container technology. Drone uses a simple YAML configuration file, a superset of docker-compose, to define and execute Pipelines inside Docker containers.
*   [Luigi (‚≠ê18k)](https://github.com/spotify/luigi) Luigi is a Python module that helps you build complex pipelines of batch jobs. It handles dependency resolution, workflow management, visualization etc. It also comes with Hadoop support built in.
items.content_html:

  • T.A.D.S. boilerplate (‚≠ê779) A boilerplate to setup a Docker Swarm environment with Ansible

Build And Release System

  • Drone CI Drone is a Continuous Delivery system built on container technology. Drone uses a simple YAML configuration file, a superset of docker-compose, to define and execute Pipelines inside Docker containers.
  • Luigi (‚≠ê18k) Luigi is a Python module that helps you build complex pipelines of batch jobs. It handles dependency resolution, workflow management, visualization etc. It also comes with Hadoop support built in.
